snippet.title: Binary Distortion || Glitch Trash Trans VN
snippet.description:
Binary Distortion is a glitch trash kinetic/visual novel exploring gender and transgender issues / themes. It was made by @riotjayne_ in Ren'Py for the #NaNoReno2015.

Art / Photographs / Screen Caps and SFX mostly sourced online and used without permission. Music used with permission by hearken (@h34rken) off Somewhere, Someday (2014) and DP / DR (2015).

Download it now from Itch.Io
https://riotjayne.itch.io/
